summary: Promo Art Featuring Brie Larson As CAPTAIN MARVEL
title: Promo Art Featuring Brie Larson As CAPTAIN MARVEL
body:
Promo Art Featuring Brie Larson As CAPTAIN MARVEL

Check out this rendering of Brie Larson as Captain Marvel from the cover of Mudo Dos Super-Herois.

No confirmation on whether or not this is “official” promotional art but Kevin Feige promises that the first teaser trailer will be released by the end of the year. Along with that will no doubt come official photos and posters.

Captain Marvel opens in theaters 03/08/19
